      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
        © 2026 Eyal Rotbart. Built with <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-teal-600 dark:hover:text-teal-400 transition-colors">Astro</a>.
